Package: EpigenicR
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Epigenomic Data Analysis and Visualization
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Nimra", "Ali",
      email = "nimra@epigenica.org",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Provides tools for processing, analyzing, and visualizing 
    epigenomic data from ChIP-seq, methylation, and chromatin state experiments.
    Includes functions for quality control, metadata management, annotation 
    retrieval, and creating comprehensive EPK (Epigenomic Package) objects
    for downstream analysis.
